    "CONTENT": {
        "Career": "In 2015, when Juričić suffered several serious knee injuries that almost ended his career, he was out for almost two years but managed to recover and continue his career.On 3 July 2022, Armenian Premier League club Pyunik announced the signing of Juričić. On 8 February 2023, Juričić extended his contract with Pyunik until the end of the 2023/24 season.On 22 August 2023, Juričić signed for Romanian Liga I club CFR Cluj.On 19 January 2024, Juričić returned to Pyunik on loan for the rest of the season.",
