    "SUMMARY": "Luka Juričić (born 25 November 1996) is a professional footballer who plays as a striker for Armenian Premier League club Pyunik, on loan from Liga I club CFR Cluj. Born in Germany, he has represented Bosnia and Herzegovina at under-19 level."
